是楚门的世界吧。"]]},"created_time":1709621577351,"last_edited_time":1709622195221,"parent_id":"0f34a3a1-4aac-4b67-9966-09bdfa7cab3e","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"7e11664a-dc18-4082-8427-6c15e2dd94f7":{"value":{"id":"7e11664a-dc18-4082-8427-6c15e2dd94f7","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1709622366770,"last_edited_time":1709622366770,"parent_id":"0f34a3a1-4aac-4b67-9966-09bdfa7cab3e","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"d480df74-423c-45a8-bcbe-b39262468dbc":{"value":{"id":"d480df74-423c-45a8-bcbe-b39262468dbc","version":525,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["每个人都受到活动空间的局限，还有认知的局限，都被笼罩在一个圈定范围内，只有不断的去打破、突破边界，才能发现世界真的很大。"]]},"created_time":1709621811808,"last_edited_time":1709622231287,"parent_id":"0f34a3a1-4aac-4b67-9966-09bdfa7cab3e","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"eb1b1149-28ef-4652-a9e1-414dbd862257":{"value":{"id":"eb1b1149-28ef-4652-a9e1-414dbd862257","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1709622365097,"last_edited_time":1709622365097,"parent_id":"0f34a3a1-4aac-4b67-9966-09bdfa7cab3e","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"e2f2345c-ccef-4aeb-9468-17a95c748b82":{"value":{"id":"e2f2345c-ccef-4aeb-9468-17a95c748b82","version":1046,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["总说“有钱人的世界你想象不到”，是真的想象不到。因为在普通人的眼里，终其一生，不过是吃喝拉撒，钱再多也过做着相同的事。父母总是用这样的话来规劝子女要遵循他们的脚步：早点结婚、生子、好好工作，周而复始，去过能被想象的生活。"]]},"created_time":1709621885835,"last_edited_time":1709622494073,"parent_id":"0f34a3a1-4aac-4b67-9966-09bdfa7cab3e","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"18dba7a7-99e7-4586-b917-ed6d64ebe203":{"value":{"id":"18dba7a7-99e7-4586-b917-ed6d64ebe203","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1709622002865,"last_edited_time":1709622002865,"parent_id